### Component 3: File Automation Settings View

#### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///c:/Users/ba/OneDrive/жЎҢйқў/exam/docs/index.html)

**HTML:** Add new `<div id="view-file-settings" class="view">` after `view-editor`, containing:
- Back button (вҶҗ иҝ”еӣһ)
- Title: рҹ“Ғ жӘ”жЎҲиҮӘеӢ•еҢ–иЁӯе®ҡ
- Horizontal pipeline visualization:
  ```
  Google Drive (ијүе…Ҙ) в”Җв”ҖвҶ’ рҹҢҗ Web в”Җв”ҖвҶ’ Google Drive (е„Іеӯҳ)
  ```
- Left node: Load folder picker button + current folder display
- Center: Web icon/label
- Right node: Save folder picker button
- Toggle switch: "иҮӘеӢ•ијүе…ҘиҲҮе„ІеӯҳеҸҜд»Ҙз”ЁдёҚеҗҢиіҮж–ҷеӨҫ"
- Status text showing current folder configuration

**CSS:** Pipeline layout styles, toggle switch styles

**JS:**
- `initFileSettings()` вҖ” reads localStorage and populates UI
- Toggle handler for `brain_separate_folders` localStorage key
- Reuses existing [openDrivePicker()](file:///c:/Users/ba/OneDrive/%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2/exam/docs/index.html#3107-3226) with minor adaptation for load/save distinction
- [switchView('view-file-settings')](file:///c:/Users/ba/OneDrive/%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2/exam/docs/index.html#2167-2175) integration
- Persist `brain_load_folder_id`, `brain_save_folder_id`, `brain_separate_folders` to localStorage

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification (Browser)

1. **Open [index.html](file:///c:/Users/ba/OneDrive/%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2/exam/docs/index.html) in localhost** вҖ” verify the 4-column habit loop canvas appears after initialization
2. **Add nodes** вҖ” click "вһ• ж–°еўһжҸҗзӨә" etc., verify nodes appear in correct columns
3. **Connect nodes** вҖ” drag from one node to another, verify SVG arrow appears
4. **Delete nodes/edges** вҖ” use delete buttons, verify cleanup
5. **Open вҳ° menu** вҖ” verify it shows рҹ“Ғ жӘ”жЎҲиҮӘеӢ•еҢ–иЁӯе®ҡ, рҹ“Ҙ жүӢеӢ•еҢҜе…Ҙ, рҹ’ҫ жүӢеӢ•еӯҳжӘ”
6. **Click "рҹ’ҫ жүӢеӢ•еӯҳжӘ”"** вҖ” verify JSON file downloads
7. **Click "рҹ“Ҙ жүӢеӢ•еҢҜе…Ҙ"** вҖ” verify file picker opens
8. **Click "рҹ“Ғ жӘ”жЎҲиҮӘеӢ•еҢ–иЁӯе®ҡ"** вҖ” verify settings view appears
9. **Toggle switch** вҖ” verify separate folder picker shows/hides
10. **Back button** вҖ” verify returns to canvas
11. **Open `old.html`** вҖ” verify full original tree canvas + editor + auth works
